AUDIO: 'generation, for example, if we add like these three Loras, traditionally, these Loras would fight or conflict with each other. This would cause a ton of errors or glitches or distortion like this. And that\'s because when you use multiple'

[20:11] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Loras, one character\'s face might bleed into another, some styles might overwrite other styles. The model gets confused about what belongs where, and previously, there isn\'t really a nice solution to this. But, for Free Fuse, this is a training-free framework that'

[20:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'solves this problem. And so, with Free Fuse, even if you input a ton of Loras like different characters at the top here, plus different props on this left column, you can add like many of these at once into your image, and you won\'t'

[20:39] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
